reviews.text: Be careful travelling from this station, several times they have delays. It can be useful if you're close to it but if you can go to Clapham junction station instead will be always better.

I wish I could give minus star to this horrible station. 
The train services is very bad specially on the weekend .i recommend avoid travel  from this station .its better to walk or catch the bus to Clapham junction rather than wasting time waiting for no train.or several delayed and finally cancel 😏

Very pretty, cosy suburban station with surprisingly frequent trains in both directions. When I first visited, I expected a half-hourly service but it receives 8 per hour, which was a welcome treat.

Bus connections go all the way to Kensal Rise and Tooting, the area outside the station has a pleasant vibe to it and station staff are always willing to help.
